headline: KEYCORP TO PRESENT AT THE GOLDMAN SACHS FINANCIAL SERVICES CONFERENCE
summary: KeyCorp (NYSE: KEY) announced today that Chris Gorman, Chairman and Chief Executive Officer, will speak at the Goldman Sachs Financial Services Conference on Tuesday, December 10, 2024, at 11:20 a.m. ET in New York City.
